### 1) CREATE VEHICLE
POST http://localhost:8090/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "providerId": 1,
  "type": "E_SCOOTER",
  "description": "Test scooter",
  "pricePerUnit": 1.5,
  "billingModel": "PER_HOUR",
  "currentLatitude": 51.5,
  "currentLongitude": 7.4
}

###
### 2) GET VEHICLE BY ID
GET http://localhost:8090/vehicles/1

###
### 3) UPDATE LOCATION
PUT http://localhost:8090/vehicles/1/location
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 51.51,
  "longitude": 7.41
}

###
### 4) UPDATE STATUS
PUT http://localhost:8090/vehicles/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "BOOKED"
}

###
### 5) FULL UPDATE
PUT http://localhost:8090/vehicles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "E_CAR",
  "description": "Updated vehicle",
  "pricePerUnit": 2.0,
  "billingModel": "PER_KILOMETER",
  "maxDurationMinutes": 120,
  "maxKilometers": 50,
  "minAge": 18,
  "maxPersons": 2
}

###
### 6) SEARCH AVAILABLE VEHICLES
GET http://localhost:8090/vehicles/available?lat=51.5&lon=7.4&radius=1
